data.title: 1969 Press Photo Prime Minister and Mrs. Eisaku Sato of Japan leave Airport
data.meta_description: This is an original press photo. Photo is dated 11-18-1969. A: The short answer is no. Q: What are your office hours?. We are open M-F 9 to 5 (CST). It may contain wrinkles, cracks, and possibly even tears due to its age and how it was handled before it got to us.
